Local expertise and a commitment to personal attention is what you'll find at Sullivan & Company Real Estate. Whether you're planning to buy or sell, our team of committed professionals has the experience and the know-how to help you achieve all of your real estate goals.
Our community-based company offers free consultation on local property values, market conditions, tax assessment and abatements, building/zoning codes and more. Whether you need assistance with a residence, a parcel of land, or commercial property, we are here to help!
